  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: "Honestly? Most of the time, no. Anything interesting results in disaster
      for me. But I\u2019ve signed up to this program for a reason. I want to see
      where this goes."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dc24e77c8220d5b43bd418e911809b3b, type: 3}
    sentence: "What if I tell you it\u2019s been exactly the same for me? "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Then we will just have to make sure the disaster is a small one so
      we can move past it, make it short and painless.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Or, we can try to enjoy it. Something tells me you enjoy a bit of suffering.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Hmm, I guess I\u2019m not entirely opposed to that."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Perfect.
    eventTrigger: StartPixelGame
